  "detailed_description": "In COLORFUL GHOSTS, you'll face mind-bending challenges! Ghosts of different sizes are hungry for candies. These candies make them change color and blend with other little ghosts! Find the right combination between the ghost and the candy to complete the challenge.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/526e6225ea6ce11439d35a70507f6391.avif?t=1723166033\" width=619 height=281 /></span><br><br><br>Oops, it's not that easy! Ghosts can be stopped by blocks, doors, and holes! Find a way to use these objects to your advantage.<br><br>Is there a hole in your way? Find the <strong>right button</strong> to close it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Push the blocks with the ghost's head. And remember that you can press a button with the block!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To open a door, find the <strong>right key</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Struggling with colors? Don't worry, Colorful Ghosts features an accessibility system, <strong>ColorAdd</strong>. The symbols appearing on the ghosts, candies, and final goals will help you identify which color is there!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e55ef41e89e58bba60b3fda684580c88.avif?t=1723166033\" width=600 height=438 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/b8fd939862fefcfe3d3fe18d2b9cda4d.avif?t=1723166033\" width=619 height=181 /></span><br><br><strong>Coming soon a new world for you to play!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "In COLORFUL GHOSTS, you'll face mind-bending challenges! Ghosts of different sizes are hungry for candies. These candies make them change color and blend with other little ghosts! Find the right combination between the ghost and the candy to complete the challenge.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/526e6225ea6ce11439d35a70507f6391.avif?t=1723166033\" width=619 height=281 /></span><br><br><br>Oops, it's not that easy! Ghosts can be stopped by blocks, doors, and holes! Find a way to use these objects to your advantage.<br><br>Is there a hole in your way? Find the <strong>right button</strong> to close it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e71e84f10ee4828fb52805f02422dfc1.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Push the blocks with the ghost's head. And remember that you can press a button with the block!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/121a0b8ae994b646dfc412207b0c5a97.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To open a door, find the <strong>right key</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.poster.avif?t=1723166033\" width=400 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.webm?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/0ffbe6a5ac47df16b00d7954cb7ef958.mp4?t=1723166033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Struggling with colors? Don't worry, Colorful Ghosts features an accessibility system, <strong>ColorAdd</strong>. The symbols appearing on the ghosts, candies, and final goals will help you identify which color is there!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/e55ef41e89e58bba60b3fda684580c88.avif?t=1723166033\" width=600 height=438 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976190/extras/b8fd939862fefcfe3d3fe18d2b9cda4d.avif?t=1723166033\" width=619 height=181 /></span><br><br><strong>Coming soon a new world for you to play!</strong>",
